{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"63840-azizi-la-poupee","title":"Azizi La Poupée","description":"Read the story of my doll names Azizi and how I love to take care of him.","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Marianne Pasty Abdul Wahid"],"illustrators":["Natalie  Propa"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/63840-azizi-la-poupee"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/127080/size3/6f765a6844197d575ad1aede81f90e9e.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/127080/size6/6f765a6844197d575ad1aede81f90e9e.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93122/size6/106d02d7c24364c7e0e6f8c3ac70c0ee.jpg","text":"Voici Azizi. Azizi est\nma poupée.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93123/size6/66160bf40caf404ca14e0b9b09b01fe7.jpg","text":"J'aime beaucoup\nAzizi parce qu'elle\nsourit tout le\ntemps.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93124/size6/79126e9920f4f1a835707324f966a5b6.jpg","text":"Après m'être levée, je me lave levisage. Puis je cherche Azizi.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93125/size6/2d35321c8acf5a9aa76d3bae8bb5c244.jpg","text":"Une fois Azizi trouvée, je lui brosse ses cheveux.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93126/size6/9df061c998117a6959a3178e0d916274.jpg","text":"Lorsque je mange mon petitdéjeuner, je donne aussi à manger à Azizi.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93127/size6/a130f414bb124b9e7a6cb92758e55c52.jpg","text":"Lorsque je mange\ndes bonbons, j'en\ndonne aussi un à\nAzizi.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93128/size6/d92ffddcf3ffac79e90b0cc490e6b0e6.jpg","text":"Mais Azizi ne mange jamais son bonbon. \nJe me demande pourquoi!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93129/size6/d06ebae86ba8f0dbb56533549f99836a.jpg","text":"Je me promène dans le jardin et y cueille des fleurs.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93130/size6/b36f9c3094223af651d40a5bcf0c2833.jpg","text":"J'en donne une à Azizi. Mais elle ne dit jamais \"merci.\"","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93131/size6/dd94807cc47ad44e2d64211f1399fa68.jpg","text":"Je lave Azizi avant que ma maman ne me donne mon bain.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93132/size6/82ba568d3750da0f9d95c9e3fc97570b.jpg","text":"J'habille Azizi de vêtements rouges, parce que j'adore le rouge.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93133/size6/dee382aea7b6a9781ac7f962464d6659.jpg","text":"Lorsque je me couche, je couche Azizi près de moi.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":123}}